high_descs: turn right and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and walk over to the center of the dining table on the left
grab the cell phone off of the dining table there
turn right and walk past the table, the turn left and walk around to the other side of the table
place the cell phone down on top of a plate on the table
pick the plate up off of the table
turn around and walk over to end of the room, then turn right and walk over to the small table in between the two chairs on the right, towards the end of the room
place the plate down on the table there
anns.task_desc: place a plate with a cell phone on it on top of the table

high_descs: Look down, and walk to the table to your right to the side where an empty box sits and look down.
Grab the phone on the table.
With the phone, look up, and walk to the side of the table where the gray plate sits and look down.
Place the phone on the plate standing.
Grab the plate with the phone on it and look up.

Carrying the phone, turn around, walk straight, turn right when you reach the television stand, walk straight, turn right when you reach the fireplace and walk straight to the table between the chair and couch.
Place the plate with the phone on it on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a phone on it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around to the right and go forward. Walk forward to the table then turn right and then right again to go around to the other side of the table.
Pick the phone up from the table.
Turn to the right and then turn to the left then turn left again to go around the table to the other side.
Place the phone on the plate on the table.
Pick up the plate and the phone from the table.

Turn around and go to the left. Go to the far wall and then turn to the right. Go forward to the fireplace then turn to the right then go around the coffee table and make a left to face the side table.
Place the plate and phone on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Move the plate and phone to the side table.
